quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,17,"Ich vzor bol those zaciatok zapalit potom mat rad it zacat chliev lahky them GOD berie away ich lahky lavy them v darkness, unable see"
  2,18,Deaf dumb blind they zlyhat spatny listok
  2,19,Iny vzor rainstorm sky do there bol darkness thunder lightning They put ich fingers ich ears evade smrt! GOD bol fully aware z disbelievers
  2,20,lightning skoro chmatnut away ich eyesight. When it kypry them they move forward a when it turns dark they stand still If GOD wills He mozem berie away ich hearing ich eyesight! GOD bol Omnipotent
  2,21,O ludia kult len tvoj Lord -Jeden created ona a those before ona -Ze ona saved
  2,22,Jeden robit zem habitable ona sky zlozenie. He sends sky zavlazit produce all laskavy z ovocie tvoj sustenance. Ona nie set idols rival GOD ihned ze ona zauzlit
  2,23,Ona have any doubt zretel co my revealed our servant potom produce 1 sura mat rad these vola sa tvoj own svedok GOD ona bol truthful
  2,24,If ona nie robit this -Ona never robit this -Potom beware z Hellfire kurivo je zaludnit rocks it awaits disbelievers